# sd-upload

Upload images to Imgur

## Required

    process.env.IMGUR_ID
    process.env.IMGUR_SECRET

## Example

    var imgur = require('sd-upload');

    var params = {
      image: ''
    };

    imgur.upload(params, function(image) {
      console.log(image);
    });


## More info

https://api.imgur.com/endpoints/image
